                        <locus target="#iv(erso)" facs="002">Fol. iv(erso)</locus>
                        <desc>Child being baptized, the mother, a priest, and a deacon with a book <ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1035HolyMan">Holy Man Portrait</ref> with caption <q><foreign xml:lang="am">አጠመቀ፡</foreign></q>, and on book <q><foreign xml:lang="gez">መጽሐፈ፡ ክርስትና፡</foreign></q>
                        </desc>
                     </decoNote>
